original_title: The Canadian Tenors: Live At The Royal Conservatory Of Music Toronto
overview: Canadian Tenors Live at The Royal Conservatory Of Music in Toronto with performances from Sarah McLachlan and David Foster. 'The Canadian Tenors are following in the footsteps of my other protégés Josh Groban and Andrea Bocelli.' - David Foster.
title: The Canadian Tenors: Live At The Royal Conservatory Of Music Toronto
